INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(397,'100%% Kona Bourbon Pointu Laurina','Medium-Light','27.76','Hawai''I','Deeply and sweetly pungent; layered and intricate. Dark chocolate, raspberry, freesia, port wine, a hint of fresh, fragrant tobacco in aroma and cup. Balanced, quietly forceful in its sweet-savory structure; light but exceptionally silky in mouthfeel. All notes ring on in a layered, flavor-saturated finish.');
