INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(447,'Salvador, Kona','Medium','10.58','Hawai''I','Rich-toned, chocolaty. Dark chocolate, black cherry, gently scorched oak, molasses, gardenia in aroma and cup. Sweet in structure with very gentle acidity; crisp, velvety mouthfeel. Richly drying finish, resonant with notes of dark chocolate, gardenia and scorched oak.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(448,'Ethiopia Shantawene Washed','Medium-Light','6.17','Ethiopia','Very sweet, high-toned, richly floral. Star jasmine, lemon verbena, pineapple, cocoa nib, frankincense in aroma and cup. Sweetly tart structure with juicy, levitating acidity; delicate but syrupy mouthfeel. Crisp, long, floral-toned finish.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(449,'Organic Suke Quto Ethiopia','Medium-Light','5.58','Ethiopia','Overarchingly sweet, richly savory. Nectarine, sandalwood, marzipan, spearmint, freesia-like flowers in aroma and cup. Deeply sweet structure with a tart, vibrant acidity; nectar-like mouthfeel. Rich-toned finish with marzipan notes lingering into the long.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(450,'Karen J Kona Red Bourbon','Medium-Light','0.17','Hawai''I','Crisply fruit-centered, floral-toned. Mango, cocoa nib, lilac, honey, Meyer lemon in aroma and cup. Sweet-toned structure with lush, elegant acidity; crisply viscous mouthfeel. Balanced, layered finish.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(451,'Abu Natural Panama Geisha','Medium-Light','20.55','Panama','Deeply fruit-toned, richly chocolaty. Candied papaya, black cherry, dark chocolate, honeysuckle, agave syrup in aroma and cup. Tart-leaning structure with high-toned, fruity acidity; smooth, gently tannic mouthfeel. The finish centers on dark chocolate and black cherry.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(452,'Colombia Finca Las Margaritas Natural Sudan Rume','Medium-Light','17.64','Colombia','Sweetly fermenty, wine-toned. Lychee, dried raspberry, grappa, dark chocolate fudge, lily in aroma and cup. Sweetly tart structure with crisp, citrusy acidity; delicate, silky-smooth mouthfeel. Finish consolidates to notes of dried raspberry, grappa and dark chocolate.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(453,'Ethiopia Konga','Medium','5.29','Ethiopia','Crisply sweet, floral- and fruit-toned. Peach, narcissus, almond butter, nougat, cedar in aroma and cup. In structure sweetly and gently tart, with a balanced and roundly bright acidity. Satiny, lively mouthfeel. Peach and flowers linger in the finish.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(454,'Gesha Village Single-Variety Gesha Special Selection','Medium-Light','13.23','Ethiopia','Deeply rich, balanced, fruit- and floral-toned. Tea rose, pomelo, dark chocolate, pie cherry, fresh-cut oak in aroma and cup. Sweet-tart structure with round, fruit-toned acidity; rich, satiny mouthfeel. Tea rose, pie cherry and dark chocolate saturate the resonant finish.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(455,'DR Congo Muungano','Medium-Light','5.88','Democratic Republic Of The Congo','Richly sweet-tart, earth-toned. Blood orange, pipe tobacco, roasted almond, rhododendron, baking chocolate in aroma and cup. Tart-leaning structure with crisp, green-apple-like (malic) acidity; deep, velvety mouthfeel. The richly drying finish consolidates to blood orange and pipe tobacco.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(456,'Colombian','Medium-Light','5.86','Colombia','Bold, rich, confident. Strawberry, magnolia, baking chocolate, fresh-cut fir, maple syrup in aroma and cup. Deeply sweet structure with brisk acidity; saturating, satiating mouthfeel. A gentle decrescendo of all cup attributes carries into the pleasing finish.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(457,'Suyusama Colombia','Medium-Light','5.58','Colombia','Cocoa-toned, crisply sweet. Cocoa powder, hazelnut butter, pear, cedar, agave syrup in aroma and cup. Sweet in structure with brisk acidity; velvety mouthfeel. The finish consolidates to notes of hazelnut and pear with undertones of cocoa powder.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(458,'Ethiopia BergWu SP Series: Wuri Red Cherries 19/EXP02','Medium','8.46','Ethiopia','Deeply sweet, fruit-forward. Grape candy, dark chocolate, grappa barrel, fresh-cut fir, gardenia in aroma and cup. Sweet-tart structure with gentle acidity; full, satiny mouthfeel. Crisp, dry, chocolaty finish with notes of sweet grape wafting up in the long, as well as sweet alcohol ferment.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(459,'Ka’u Giant Maragogipe','Medium-Light','12.35','Hawai''I','Deep-toned, sweet-savory. Nectarine, narcissus, hop flowers, sandalwood, honey in aroma and cup. Richly sweet structure with gentle, round but engaging acidity; plush, syrupy mouthfeel. The richly bittersweet finish centers on honey and hop flowers in the short with nectarine returning in the long. ');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(460,'Wood Valley Single Estate Ka’u','Medium-Light','10.58','Hawai''I','Richly floral- and nut-toned. Freesia-like flowers, almond brittle, baking chocolate, black cherry, fresh-cut oak in aroma and cup. Deeply sweet structure with tart, lively acidity; full, satiny mouthfeel. Finish consolidates around almond brittle and freesia. ');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(461,'Kona Maragogype','Medium','17.64','Hawai''I','Deep-toned, richly sweet-savory. Dark chocolate, hop flowers, lychee, sandalwood, almond brittle in aroma and cup. Sweet-savory structure with round, gentle acidity; plush, creamy mouthfeel. The resonant finish is redolent with notes of almond brittle and lychee.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(462,'Organic Ethiopia Agaro-Nano Challa','Medium-Light','6.75','Ethiopia','Delicately sweet, high-toned, citrusy. Key lime, cocoa nib, strawberry, freesia-like flowers, cedar in aroma and cup. Sweetly tart structure with juicy, vibrant acidity; lush, creamy mouthfeel. The finish consolidates to sweet fruit notes (berries and citrus) and cocoa nib.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(463,'Guatemala Vista Al Bosque','Medium','5.58','Guatemala','Chocolaty, floral-toned. Dark chocolate, rhododendron-like flowers, hazelnut butter, date, cedar in aroma and cup. Sweet in structure with gentle, round acidity; very full, syrupy mouthfeel. The finish centers around notes of dark chocolate and rhododendron with hints of cedar.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(464,'Peaberry Medium Roast','Medium','13.23','Hawai''I','Rich-toned, chocolaty and floral. Baking chocolate, magnolia, agave syrup, hazelnut butter, cedar in aroma and cup. Sweet structure with gentle, round acidity; full, velvety mouthfeel. Finish consolidates to notes of baking chocolate and magnolia in the short, cedar and hazelnut in the crisp long.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(465,'Kenya Embu Gicherori Factory AA Top','Medium-Light','9.28','Kenya','Sweetly and roundly bright, high-toned, floral. Star jasmine, tangerine zest, red currant, elm, a hint of coriander in aroma and cup. Sweetly tart structure with vibrant, juicy acidity; crisp yet buoyant, syrupy mouthfeel. The richly flavor-saturated finish carries all the notes of the cup straight through into the long, particularly jasmine and red currant.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(466,'Colombia Huila Los Lagos Washed Geisha','Medium-Light','6.37','Colombia','Richly floral-toned. Baking chocolate, jasmine, tea rose, golden raisin, sandalwood in aroma and cup. Sweet in structure with brisk acidity; velvety-smooth mouthfeel. The crisp finish centers around tea rose and sandalwood notes.');
