INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(494,'Ethiopia Natural Guji Lot D Minor','Medium-Light','3.89','Ethiopia','Delicate, high-toned, richly floral. Lilac, cocoa nib, dried apricot, sandalwood, a hint of coconut in aroma and cup. Sweet-tart structure with juicy acidity; plush, syrupy mouthfeel. Rich, deeply aromatic finish that carries over all the notes from the cup; lilac and cocoa nib, in particular.');
