INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(502,'Ethiopia Guji Hambela Buku Abel Natural G1','Medium-Light','5.77','Ethiopia','Fruit-forward, sweetly nut-toned. Blueberry, almond butter, baking chocolate, narcissus, cedar in aroma and cup. Sweet-toned structure with gentle, round acidity; full, creamy mouthfeel. The resonant finish centers around notes of blueberry and baking chocolate with undertones of cedar.');
