INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(504,'Ethiopia Yirgacheffe Harfusa G1','Medium-Light','5.82','Ethiopia','Delicately sweet, spicy. Apricot, freesia-like flowers, hazelnut butter, pink peppercorn, cocoa nib in aroma and cup. Sweet-toned structure with lively, citrusy acidity; silky-smooth mouthfeel. Finish consolidates to notes of apricot and pink peppercorn supported by cocoa nib. ');
