INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(710,'Indonesia Golden Sumatra TP Espresso','Medium','7.2','Indonesia','Evaluated as espresso. Complex, multi-layered, richly deep. Honeysuckle, dark chocolate, dried apricot, perique fermented pipe tobacco, pistachio in aroma and small cup. Viscous, creamy mouthfeel; resonant, long, flavor-saturated finish. The milk shot is floral, chocolaty and stone fruit-driven in equal measure.');
INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(711,'Ethiopia Suke Quto Single-Origin Espresso','Medium-Light','5.58','Ethiopia','Evaluated as espresso. Richly fruit-centered, deeply aromatic. Raspberry, dark chocolate, sandalwood, narcissus, lemon verbena in aroma and small cup. Plush, viscous mouthfeel; fruit- and floral-toned finish. In three parts milk, spice-toned sweet florals preside, with support from rich chocolate notes.');
