INSERT INTO reviews VALUE(1106,'Fruit Bomb/Ethiopia Shantewene','Medium-Light','11.02','Ethiopia','Evaluated as espresso. Aromatically intense, sweet-tart-savory. Concord grape, lychee, dark chocolate, aloewood, oregano in aroma and cup. Creamy-smooth mouthfeel; savory, herbaceous, chocolaty finish. In three parts milk, savory notes usurp sweet, with inviting aloewood and oregano notes supported by dark chocolate and lychee undertones.');
